cellProps.description: The props for the table cell.

columnFilters.description: The column filters state of the table.

defaultColumnFilters.description: The default column filters state of the table.

defaultPagination.description: The default pagination state of the table.

defaultRowSelection.description: The default row selection state of the table.

defaultSorting.description: The default sorting state of the table.

enableAutoResizeTableWidth.description: If `true`, the table width will be automatically resized to the content.

enableKeyboardNavigation.description: If `true`, the keyboard navigation will be enabled.

enablePagination.description: If `true`, the pagination will be enabled.

footerGroupProps.description: The props for the table footer group.

footerProps.description: The props for the table footer.

headerCheckboxProps.description: The props for the table header checkbox.

headerGroupProps.description: The props for the table header group.

headerProps.description: The props for the table header.

highlightOnHover.description: If `true`, highlight the row when the table row is hovered.

highlightOnSelected.description: If `true`, highlight the row when the table row is selected.

initialFocusableCell.description: The initial focusable cell of the table.

onColumnFiltersChange.description: The callback invoked when the column filters state changes.

onPaginationChange.description: The callback invoked when the pagination state changes.

onRowClick.description: The callback invoked when the row is clicked.

onRowDoubleClick.description: The callback invoked when the row is double clicked.

onSortingChange.description: The callback invoked when the sorting state changes.

pagination.description: The pagination state of the table.

resizableTriggerProps.description: The props for the resizable trigger.

rowCheckboxProps.description: The props for the table row checkbox.

rowProps.description: The props for the table row.

rowSelection.description: The row selection state of the table.

scrollAreaProps.description: The props for the scroll area.

selectOnClickRow.description: If `true`, the row will be selected when the row is clicked.

sorting.description: The sorting state of the table.

sortingIcon.description: The sorting icon of the table.

sortingIconProps.description: The props for the sorting icon.

tbodyProps.description: The props for the table tbody.

tfootProps.description: The props for the table tfoot.

theadProps.description: The props for the table thead.

withBorder.description: If `true`, display the outer border of the table.

withCheckbox.description: If `true`, the table will have a checkbox column.

withColumnBorders.description: If `true`, display line on the columns of the table.

withFooterCheckbox.description: If `true`, the table will have a checkbox in the footer.

withFooterGroups.description: If `true`, the table will have footer groups.

withScrollArea.description: Whether to enable the scroll area.
